source to separate the drug barons from the drug money weve 
got to hit the drug lords where it counts its time to take the 
profit out of the drug trade 
he also lauded treasurys role in sustaining our longrunning 
economic expansion restructuring our savings and loans and 
helping solve the third worlds debt problems 
