services were in a shoddy state he proposed allowing private 
services to compete with governmentrun institutions privatizing 
public companies and limiting immigration which he says norway 
cannot afford 
despite her international reputation as a conservationist mrs 
brundtland also was attacked for alleged laxness toward pollution of 
norways fjords 
