exchanges report that copper stocks in the exchangeapproved 
warehouse had risen last week by 4800 metric tons an unexpectedly 
large increase 
the big buildup in lme stocks appeared to contradict the 
tightsupply fears that have provided the main support for coppers 
price during the past 1 months 
