ltd if its nevadabased distributing company promises not to sell 
video poker machines that igt claimed were copies of its players 
edge machine 
under the stipulation igt has until next monday to amend its 
lawsuit to continue the dispute if after examining universals 
redesigned video poker machine it decides universals new machine 
does duplicate igts players edge game 
donald lattin attorney for universal co said he doesnt 
believe igt will pursue the lawsuit because universals video 
poker machine is substantially different than igts 
all of the video poker machines look basically alike on the 
outside lattin said its like buying a refrigerator therere 
lots of different brands but they look the same 
